main event: A flight of four UFO objects were observed over the West End area of New Jersey on September 9, 1964.
interesting points: The objects were reddish-orange in color and flashed at a rate of 2-3 flashes per second., The objects moved horizontally and maintained their elevation throughout the observation., Reports indicate sightings of up to 10 objects over a two-hour period., Observations included glowing and fast-moving objects with varied shapes., The sightings were reported by numerous reliable sources, but no confirmed witnesses were recorded.
